    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Swedish variation of Jugend and Art Nouveau, more restrained than eleswhere in Europe. Characterized by a more naturalistic ornamentation, inspired by the Swedish flora and fauna; in later years, exhibited more geometric design.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
